records.name: Fuvahmulah Central Hotel

descriptions.direction: Located in Fuvahmulah, Fuvahmulah Central Hotel is in the city center and on the beach. Fuvahmulah Harbor and Hulhudhoo Harbor are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Dhadimagu Lake and Fuvahmulah Beach. Koagannu Park and Huludu Lagoon Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. Snorkeling, windsurfing, and fishing offer great chances to get out on the surrounding water, or you can seek out an adventure with hiking/biking trails nearby.
descriptions.general: Located in Fuvahmulah, Fuvahmulah Central Hotel offers 4-star accommodations with a fitness center, a garden and a terrace. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests. At the hotel, each room is equipped with a closet. Complete with a private bathroom equipped with a shower and free toiletries, guest rooms at Fuvahmulah Central Hotel have a flat-screen TV and air conditioning, and some rooms are equipped with a balcony. All rooms will provide guests with a desk and a coffee machine. Breakfast is available, and includes buffet, continental and Asian options. At the accommodation you'll find a restaurant serving American cuisine. Vegetarian, halal and gluten-free options can also be requested. The area is popular for cycling, and bike rental and car rental are available at Fuvahmulah Central Hotel. There's a business center and guests can also use the ironing service or dry cleaning service. Fuvahmulah Airport is 0.6 miles away.
